Description: Flexible and user-friendly probabilistic segmentation of time series with 
    regime changes by a regression model governed by a hidden Markov process, fitted by the 
    Baum-Welch (EM) algorithm. See also the packages 'RHLP', 'PWR', and 'MHMMR'.
